name: Victoria Walsh
summary: Victoria Walsh is a 32-year-old straight woman located in Los Angeles, California. She is a software engineer in the technology industry and graduated from Columbia University. She is originally from Austin, Texas, and speaks three languages: English, Spanish, and French. She values honesty, kindness, creativity, and personal growth. Victoria enjoys outdoor activities, coding, photography, and reading. She is agnostic and politically liberal. She is seeking a long-term, monogamous relationship. She does not currently have children but is open to having them in the future. Victoria is a cat owner, and a Cancer by astrological sign. She is an INTJ according to the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator. Victoria sometimes drinks alcohol, and she does not smoke or use marijuana. Fitness is a part of her routine. She is interested in a man between the ages of 30 to 40 who is similarly active, a non-smoker, and open to having children.
